OL,3,C'Mum was denied chance of survival':
OL,4,CMan says medic 'played God'
OL,6,FA man from Coleraine has told the
OL,7,FCovid-19 Inquiry that he believes his
OL,8,Fmother was denied the chance of
OL,9,Fsurvival in April 2020.
OL,11,FGlen Grundle spoke about his mum
OL,12,FMilda's experience in hospital,
OL,13,Fdescribing "issues at all levels", and
OL,14,Fcalling for accountability.
OL,16,FHe was among a number of members of
OL,17,Fthe Northern Ireland Covid-19 Bereaved
OL,18,FFamilies for Justice group to give
OL,19,Fevidence to the latest module of the
OL,20,FUK Covid-19 Inquiry on Tuesday.
OL,26,@uD@LOUuD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
