CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772640680
OL,3,C'Mum was denied chance of survival':
OL,4,CMan says medic 'played God'
OL,6,FMr Grundle gave evidence on the impact
OL,7,Fof Covid-19 restrictions on funerals
OL,8,Fand wakes in Northern Ireland,
OL,9,Fdescribing the coming together of
OL,10,Ffamilies and friends to share memories
OL,11,Fas "very much part of the culture
OL,12,Fhere".
OL,14,FHe also described examples of the
OL,15,Fimpact of "pandemic grief", such as
OL,16,Fhim not having given anyone a "proper
OL,17,Fhug" since the last time he saw his
OL,18,Fmother.
OL,26,@sD@DOUtD@EO]wD@KOUwD@ZO]xD@_OUyD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
