OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772640680
OL,3,C'Mum was denied chance of survival':
OL,4,CMan says medic 'played God'
OL,6,FAppearing remotely before the inquiry
OL,7,Fin London, Mr Grundle said his mother,
OL,8,FMilda, who had MS, was taken to
OL,9,Fhospital in early April 2020 and said
OL,10,Fshe was "immediately put under
OL,11,Fpressure" to agree to a do-not-
OL,12,Fresuscitate (DNR) order.
OL,14,FMr Grundle told the inquiry that a
OL,15,Fconsultant said his mother had "no
OL,16,Fquality of life" because she used a
OL,17,Fhoist and had carers.
OL,26,@rD@IOUsD@IO]wD@`OUxD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772640680
OL,3,C'Mum was denied chance of survival':
OL,4,CMan says medic 'played God'
OL,6,F"I was absolutely shocked, I argued
OL,7,Fwith him on the telephone, I told him
OL,8,Fthat there would be repercussions. I
OL,9,Fcouldn't believe someone was playing
OL,10,FGod, which can never be allowed to
OL,11,Fhappen," he said.
OL,13,F"Quality of life is something only
OL,14,Fthat person knows."
OL,16,FHe said he started emailing
OL,17,Fpoliticians and doing media interviews
OL,18,Fto highlight his concerns, and said
OL,19,Fthat the consultant was later removed
OL,20,Ffrom his mother's case.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@HO]uD@AOUvD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
