PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772640680
OL,3,C'Mum was denied chance of survival':
OL,4,CMan says medic 'played God'
OL,6,FHowever, he said there were continued
OL,7,Fefforts to get his mother to agree to
OL,8,Fa DNR, adding she accepted to a
OL,9,Fcertain extent when they told her she
OL,10,Fwouldn't get a ventilator in the
OL,11,Fintensive care unit.
OL,13,FAt that time, he said there were
OL,14,Fwarnings in the media about the health
OL,15,Fservice being short of resources,
OL,16,Fadding hospitals were "terrified at
OL,17,Fthe anticipated tsunami of patients"
OL,18,Fthat they had seen in other countries.
OL,26,@xD@WOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
