PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772640680
OL,3,C'Mum was denied chance of survival':
OL,4,CMan says medic 'played God'
OL,6,F"It's my personal belief that my mum
OL,7,Fwas denied a chance at survival," he
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"The DNR has room for three signatures
OL,11,Fand only one consultant signed it,
OL,12,Fthere were supposed to be three
OL,13,Fdifferent people involved in the
OL,14,Fassessment, and I don't consider it
OL,15,Fvalid ... of course, I didn't have
OL,16,Faccess to the hospital, so I didn't
OL,17,Fknow what was going on."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@aO]rD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
