PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772640680
OL,3,C'Mum was denied chance of survival':
OL,4,CMan says medic 'played God'
OL,6,FMr Grundle said he wants answers about
OL,7,Fhis mother's care and how she got
OL,8,FCovid-19, adding he has been
OL,9,Fcampaigning for an inquest into her
OL,10,Fdeath.
OL,12,F"I really haven't started to grieve
OL,13,F... if we can't even get information,
OL,14,Fto accept what has happened, to
OL,15,Funderstand," he said.
OL,17,F"You see this with Hillsborough as
OL,18,Fwell, the families' pain is prolonged,
OL,19,Fthat's why the work on the duty of
OL,20,Fcandour is so important.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@LO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/8
