OL,3,C'Mum was denied chance of survival':
OL,4,CMan says medic 'played God'
OL,6,F"Truth, accountability and justice for
OL,7,Fmy mum, and that's what we want."
OL,9,FMarie McArdle and Julie McMurray are
OL,10,Falso giving evidence to the inquiry on
OL,11,FTuesday.
